<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(صحيح)</span> <span class="c2">(خ ن)</span> عن ابن عباس. <span class="c2">(الإرواء ٢٠٩٦)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٣٠٧٧ - المختلعات هن المنافقات <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(صحيح)</span> <span class="c2">(ت)</span> عن ثوبان. <span class="c2">(الصحيحة ٦٣٣)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
