<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(صحيح)</span> <span class="c2">(طب)</span> عقبة بن عامر. <span class="c2">(الصحيحة ١٦٣٣)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
